Mr. Benishek (for himself, Mr. Amodei, Mr. Gosar, Mr. Young of Alaska, Mr. Buchanan, Mr. Simpson, Ms. Jenkins, Mr. Hanna, Mr. Daines, and Mr. Hudson) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the Committee on Natural Resources, and in addition to the Committee on Agriculture, for a period to be subsequently determined by the Speaker, in each case for consideration of such provisions as fall within the jurisdiction of the committee concerned
